      "review_summary": "The branch scopes Claude OAuth delegated refresh and version detection to app runtime, adds bounded Claude web fallback/cancellation and OAuth history ownership handling, and expands focused Swift/Linux coverage.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source inspection gives a high-confidence path for the OAuth side-effect bug: current main can delegate Claude OAuth refresh in CLI runtime and probe Claude version after OAuth results. I did not run live Claude/OAuth/Keychain probes because repository policy avoids real account prompts unless explicitly requested.",
